This paper is about deep reinforcement learning and regularization techniques for policy optimization algorithms. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on training neural networks for control tasks. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics), as the paper discusses the performance of RL algorithms on control tasks. Additionally, the paper mentions using regularization techniques in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY), which are also relevant sub-categories.
